        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <h1 class="primary-title">Pixel Craft Season #6</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col info text-center">
                <h2>Dragon's Breath Green Shulker Box</h2>
                <div class="col justify-content-center">
                    <img src="/images/pixel-craft/season-6/item-combinations/dragons-breath/green_shulker_box.png" alt="An image of the contents of the Green Shulker Box for the Dragon's Breath."/>
                    <p>This is what is required for the Green Shulker Box in the Dragon's Breath item. A text list of what is in the Green Shulker Box.</p>
